OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer
OL,8,FThe Speaker of the House of Commons
OL,9,FSir Lindsay Hoyle is under pressure on
OL,10,FWednesday evening.
OL,12,FThe vote resulted in MPs passing
OL,13,FLabour's amendment calling for an
OL,14,F"immediate humanitarian ceasefire"
OL,15,Famid scenes of chaos after Sir Lindsay
OL,16,Fupended parliamentary convention by
OL,17,Fselecting Labour's bid to amend an SNP
OL,18,Fmotion.
