OL,3,CCommons Speaker Sir Lindsay Hoyle
OL,4,Cunder pressure - what happens next?
OL,6,FIf no candidate received more than
OL,7,Fhalf of the votes, the candidate with
OL,8,Fthe fewest votes is eliminated, along
OL,9,Fwith anybody who received fewer than
OL,10,F5% of the votes, and MPs vote again.
OL,12,FSir Lindsay only served as Speaker for
OL,13,Fa couple of weeks after being elected
OL,14,Fbefore the last general election on
OL,15,FNovember 4, 2019, and he was then
OL,16,Freinstalled in the position in
OL,17,FDecember.
